snippet.textDisplay: Finally a clean copy of this song without the screwed up emulation. The beginning part definitely creeps you out and fitting for the creepy forest level (not so much for the flea pit levels). The chill, almost gangsta beat that drops at 1:00 just threw me off when I first heard it, like dammmmnn. Then it jumps back to creepy mode, with organs blazing. Another great track out of many for Plok. I still have the old SNES cartridge.
